{"title": "Reviews", "text": "Product Review\n\nThe Radster Road Is a Fresh Start for Rad Power Bikes\n\nRad Power Bikes\u2019 new bikes have a renewed focus on safety, with encapsulated batteries, class switching, and now \u2026 turn signals.", "authors": "['Cond\u00e9 Nast', 'Adrienne So', 'Chris Haslam', 'Nena Farrell', 'Joe Ray', 'Parker Hall', 'Christopher Null', 'Eric Ravenscraft', 'Oliver Hazelwood', 'Ryan Waniata']", "top_image": "https://media.wired.com/photos/66202cd5cd5bd3662043705d/16:9/w_1280,c_limit/Rad-Power-Bikes-Radster-Road-collage-SOURCE-Adrienne-So.jpg", "keywords": "[]", "summary": ""}
